Correct ECU is 071906021B  Bosch 0280000194/5

Bosch never produced a rebuilt version

These aren't easy to find..........

To add insult to injury, you'll have to either modify the existing FI
Harness or get a 80-83.5 FI Calif Harness for it to work properly.

